{"type":"message","id":"a5a3d022","parentId":"e3f7f27b","timestamp":"2026-03-04T03:41:02.017Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The tool ID doesn't exist anymore or has been removed. This explains why the parameters aren't being accepted - the tool is no longer available on QVeris.\n\nGiven all these issues with QVeris Finnhub tools, I should inform the user about the situation. The Finnhub news tools appear to be unavailable or broken in the current QVeris environment, and I cannot fetch the news with popularity scores as requested.\n\nLet me summarize the findings and inform the user that:\n1. The user specifically requested Finnhub news with热度≥80\n2. The Finnhub news tools in QVeris are either broken or unavailable\n3. Alternative financial news tools were tried but don't provide the same \"popularity/heat\" metric\n\nI should send a message to the user explaining this.","thinkingSignature":"b8c5e1161cca4af54dbb2d4fa03aebc889e9d88ff593ecf58328a03c4de17434"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，当前QVeris环境中的Finnhub新闻工具似乎不可用或已下架。我尝试了多种方法：\n\n1. **Finnhub新闻工具** - 多个版本 (`finnhub.news.retrieve.v1`, `finnhub.news.retrieve.v1.51b2567e`, `finnhub.market.news.list.v1`) 均报错 \"缺少必需的查询参数: 'category'\"，即使已正确传递参数\n\n2. **Alpha Vantage新闻情感工具** - 同样存在参数传递问题\n\n3. **Yahoo Finance新闻** - 返回空数据\n\n4. **直接API调用** - 使用QVeris API直接调用也返回相同错误，表明工具可能在QVeris端已失效\n\n**结论**: 无法通过QVeris获取Finnhub财经新闻热度数据。建议：\n- 检查QVeris API密钥是否有效\n- 或者手动访问 https://finnhub.io/news 获取新闻\n- 或者配置其他新闻数据源\n\nNO_REPLY"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":30597,"output":362,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44943,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772595652021}}
